Description of the Files
========================

ddj.html	- The article

fw.h		- The framework header file
fw.cc		- The framework source file

Makefile	- Makefile for the sample program
mypilot.h	- Required header file for the sample program
score.cc	- The sample program
score.def	- .def file needed by pilrc for the sample program
score.rcp	- resource file needed by pilrc for the sample program
score_res.h	- resource ID header file needed by sample program

score.prc	- The compiled sample program

